summary: Successfully resolved merge conflicts between feature branch and main branch for pasta recipes React application. Merged enhanced features from main branch including About page, improved navigation, advanced filtering UI, and better code structure while preserving current PR context.
strategyUsed: Chose main branch implementation for most files due to superior functionality including enhanced navigation with mobile menu, sophisticated filter panel with active filters display, better context API with loading states, comprehensive utility functions, and improved styling. Preserved HEAD branch PR number (78) and merged PR descriptions. Used manual resolution for complex files and git checkout for straightforward cases.
